ome.datause:
This data set is contained in Microsoft Excel spreadsheets and Adobe PDF files.  &#xD;
&#xD;
"LANL_Cores_Split.xlsx" includes a [core split intervals] tab that contains Core_ID, sample_ID, depth (cm), weight (g), and notes pertaining to each core sample collected in 2013.  The [Lab descriptions] tab contains core characterization according to depth/length of each core.&#xD;
&#xD;
"UAF_Thermal_conductivity.xls" contains initial soil core thermal conductivity results for varying core depths.  This data will be updated and expanded upon as further analysis is completed.&#xD;
&#xD;
"CT_Notes_2-14_Feb_sm.pdf" includes CT scans for each sample and associated characterization by depth.  &#xD;
&#xD;
"Hydro_cjw_3-12-2014_sm.pdf" provides an overview completed by Cathy Wilson of the collaborative core processing field trip to the Richmond Field Station, CA where lab characterization analyses was conducted.
